<plot>For 9 glorious seasons, NHL2Night provided American hockey fans with definitive scores, news, and analysis. For the tail end of its run, host John Buccigross, along with analysts Barry Melrose, Ray Ferraro, and occasionally Darren Pang offered fans witty commentary, insightful analysis, and a whole lot of fun. Fans tuned in for the information, but stayed for the obscure pop-culture references and the mullets.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?386971</url></doc>
